edu.mit.ll.graphulo.pig.backend

Class AbstractGraphuloStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pig.LoadFunc
      • edu.mit.ll.graphulo.pig.backend.AbstractGraphuloStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.pig.StoreFuncInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GraphuloStorage

    public abstract class AbstractGraphuloStorage
extends org.apache.pig.LoadFunc
implements org.apache.pig.StoreFuncInterface
    A LoadStoreFunc for retrieving data from and storing data to Graphulo A Key/Val pair will be returned as tuples: (key, colfam, colqual, colvis, timestamp, value). All fields except timestamp are DataByteArray, timestamp is a long. Tuples can be written in 2 forms: (key, colfam, colqual, colvis, value) OR (key, colfam, colqual, value)
